係四百至六百左右，因為係個按揭成數問題。即係堆血肉長城之前係四百至六百嘅能力，所以個交投數跌咗，（唔係話停頓，只係跌咗，唔好用單一例子去二元論）。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭plan個上限就去到八百至一千，所以你見開盤都係類似。林鄭plan後交投又多直至啲價去到八百至一千。<br />\n<br />\n即係好多人係用八九成按入市，資金唔係真係咁充裕。<br />\n<br />\n樓價越高，個血肉長城人數就越少。<br />\n<br />\n升跌或交投停頓，咁就要取決銀紙跌得快定係堆血肉長城首期都薪金嘅增長得快。<br />\n<br />\n香港係好多有錢人，但資金實力唔夠嘅血肉長城係唔係真係咁多人？我冇數據，但根據林鄭plan嚟睇有七成嘅買家都係計到剛剛好"},{"pid":"06835311626682866499c69726cd87c540c89efe","tid":2479443,"uid":91272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a587d9192b29a8221e0463a95e3217c47fba445f","tid":2479443,"uid":22387,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"反正買唔起<br />\n升多十倍囉<br />\n希望有生之年見多次97樓爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d731ab33120eb1f8689281ca76fbde731a5bda5","tid":2479443,"uid":392181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1890927e0e95edbebda232e6203e959c6b8dd03","tid":2479443,"uid":50196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.dailyhive.com/20200122090608/Screen-Shot-2020-01-22-at-11.55.57-AM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.dailyhive.com%2F20200122090608%2FScreen-Shot-2020-01-22-at-11.55.57-AM.png&h=6c50fc43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAffordability拋離第二位一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T01:42:01.000Z","msg":"vancouver 又咪係香港人頂撚爆D樓價"},{"pid":"08880d6303a42133c9c9d15b6feeb01ef75b275f","tid":2479443,"uid":40207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4b5abb085b6968f0ce8d030d18dc8ab9fdd5e6","tid":2479443,"uid":189638,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T23:58:51.000Z","msg":"仲有大堆血肉長城，啲人恨買樓恨到死。<br />\n<br />\n當堆血肉長城消耗得七七八八，交投又會停頓，林鄭plan就要放寬到千幾